<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Order Created - Byte Beyond Persona</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f0f2f1;
      font-family: &quot;Montserrat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    "
  >
    <table
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="padding: 48px 20px"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            width="680"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              background-color: #ffffff;
              overflow: hidden;
              box-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            "
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  background-color: #000000;
                  padding: 44px 48px 28px;
                  text-align: center;
                "
              >
                <div
                  style="
                    height: 2px;
                    background: linear-gradient(
                      90deg,
                      transparent,
                      #ffcc00,
                      transparent
                    );
                    margin-bottom: 36px;
                    opacity: 0.8;
                  "
                ></div>
                <img
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhdpnfvfn/image/upload/v1769745581/byte-beyond-persona-logo_novsd8.svg"
                  alt="Byte Beyond Persona Logo"
                  style="width: 280px; height: auto; display: inline-block"
                />
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 20px 0 0;
                    font-size: 10px;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 5px;
                    font-weight: 500;
                  "
                >
                  Order Confirmation
                </p>
                <div
                  style="
                    height: 1px;
                    background: linear-gradient(
                      90deg,
                      transparent,
                      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12),
                      transparent
                    );
                    margin-top: 28px;
                  "
                ></div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  background: #f8faf9;
                  padding: 34px 48px 30px;
                  text-align: center;
                  border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                "
              >
                <h1
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 12px;
                    font-family: &quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, Georgia, serif;
                    font-size: 34px;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #0a0a0a;
                    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
                    line-height: 1.2;
                  "
                >
                  Terima Kasih,<br />
                  <span
                    style="font-weight: 600; color: #00a86b"
                  >{{firstName}}</span>
                </h1>
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    font-size: 13px;
                    color: #444444;
                    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    font-weight: 400;
                  "
                >
                  Pesanan custom Anda telah berhasil dibuat dan sedang kami
                  proses<br />dengan penuh perhatian dan dedikasi.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 44px 48px 0">
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 4px;
                    font-size: 9px;
                    color: #00a86b;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 4px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                  "
                >
                  Detail Pesanan
                </p>
                <h3
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 20px;
                    font-family: &quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, Georgia, serif;
                    font-size: 22px;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #0a0a0a;
                    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
                  "
                >
                  Informasi Order
                </h3>

                <table
                  width="100%"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="border: 1px solid #e8ece9; margin-bottom: 36px"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        width: 38%;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Order Number
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 13px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      {{orderNumber}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Status
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      <span
                        style="
                          display: inline-block;
                          padding: 3px 12px;
                          background: #000000;
                          color: #ffcc00;
                          font-size: 10px;
                          text-transform: uppercase;
                          letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                          font-weight: 600;
                        "
                      >{{orderStatus}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Created At
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{createdAt}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Delivery Type
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{deliveryType}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Delivery Distance
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{deliveryDistance}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Total Weight
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{totalWeight}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                      "
                    >
                      Notes
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{notes}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        vertical-align: top;
                      "
                    >
                      Address
                    </td>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 11px 16px;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        line-height: 1.8;
                      "
                    >
                      {{#each addressLines}}
                        <div>{{this}}</div>
                      {{/each}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 4px;
                    font-size: 9px;
                    color: #00a86b;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 4px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                  "
                >
                  Items
                </p>
                <h3
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 16px;
                    font-family: &quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, Georgia, serif;
                    font-size: 22px;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #0a0a0a;
                  "
                >
                  Daftar Produk
                </h3>

                <div style="overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 0">
                  <table
                    width="100%"
                    cellpadding="0"
                    cellspacing="0"
                    style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #e8ece9"
                  >
                    <thead>
                      <tr style="background: #000000">
                        <th
                          align="left"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #ffcc00;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          No
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="left"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #ffcc00;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Product
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="left"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #ffcc00;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Material
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="left"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #ffcc00;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Components
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="right"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #999999;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Base
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="right"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #999999;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Material
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="right"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #999999;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 500;
                            border-right: 1px solid #222;
                          "
                        >
                          Components
                        </th>
                        <th
                          align="right"
                          style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            color: #ffcc00;
                            text-transform: uppercase;
                            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                          "
                        >
                          Total
                        </th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      {{#each productRows}}
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #999;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            {{no}}
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #0a0a0a;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            <strong
                              style="
                              display: block;
                              margin-bottom: 3px;
                              font-weight: 600;
                              font-size: 12px;
                            "
                            >{{productName}}</strong>
                            <span
                              style="font-size: 10px; color: #999999"
                            >{{sku}}</span>
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #0a0a0a;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            <span
                              style="display: block; margin-bottom: 3px"
                            >{{materialName}}</span>
                            <span
                              style="font-size: 10px; color: #999999"
                            >{{materialSku}}</span>
                          </td>
                          <td
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #555;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            {{components}}
                          </td>
                          <td
                            align="right"
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #666;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            {{basePrice}}
                          </td>
                          <td
                            align="right"
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #666;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            {{materialPrice}}
                          </td>
                          <td
                            align="right"
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #666;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            {{componentPrice}}
                          </td>
                          <td
                            align="right"
                            style="
                            padding: 11px 11px;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            color: #0a0a0a;
                            border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                            vertical-align: top;
                          "
                          >
                            <strong>{{itemTotalPrice}}</strong>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      {{/each}}
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>

                <table
                  width="100%"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="border: 1px solid #e8ece9; border-top: none"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 12px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      Subtotal
                    </td>
                    <td
                      align="right"
                      style="
                        padding: 12px 16px;
                        font-size: 13px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{subtotalPrice}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 12px 16px;
                        font-size: 11px;
                        color: #555;
                        background: #f8faf9;
                        text-transform: uppercase;
                        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      Delivery Fee
                    </td>
                    <td
                      align="right"
                      style="
                        padding: 12px 16px;
                        font-size: 13px;
                        color: #0a0a0a;
                        border-top: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                      "
                    >
                      {{deliveryFee}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      style="
                        padding: 16px 16px;
                        background: #000000;
                        border-top: 3px solid #ffcc00;
                      "
                    >
                      <span
                        style="
                          font-size: 11px;
                          color: #ffcc00;
                          text-transform: uppercase;
                          letter-spacing: 2px;
                          font-weight: 600;
                        "
                      >Grand Total</span>
                    </td>
                    <td
                      align="right"
                      style="
                        padding: 16px 16px;
                        background: #000000;
                        border-top: 3px solid #ffcc00;
                      "
                    >
                      <strong
                        style="
                          font-size: 20px;
                          color: #ffcc00;
                          font-family:
                            &quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, Georgia, serif;
                          font-weight: 500;
                          letter-spacing: 0.5px;
                        "
                      >{{grandTotalPrice}}</strong>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 40px 48px 40px">
                <table
                  width="100%"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="
                    border: 1px solid #e8ece9;
                    border-left: 3px solid #00a86b;
                    background: #f8faf9;
                  "
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 28px 32px; text-align: center">
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0 0 4px;
                          font-size: 9px;
                          color: #00a86b;
                          text-transform: uppercase;
                          letter-spacing: 4px;
                          font-weight: 600;
                        "
                      >
                        Crafted with care
                      </p>
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0 0 14px;
                          font-family:
                            &quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, Georgia, serif;
                          font-size: 20px;
                          color: #0a0a0a;
                          font-weight: 400;
                          line-height: 1.6;
                        "
                      >
                        Setiap detail pesanan Anda kami jaga<br />dengan standar
                        tertinggi.
                      </p>
                      <div
                        style="
                          width: 32px;
                          height: 2px;
                          background: #00a86b;
                          margin: 0 auto 16px;
                        "
                      ></div>
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          font-size: 11px;
                          color: #888;
                          line-height: 1.9;
                          font-weight: 300;
                          letter-spacing: 0.3px;
                        "
                      >
                        Tim kami akan segera menghubungi Anda jika diperlukan
                        konfirmasi lebih lanjut.<br />
                        Terima kasih telah mempercayakan kebutuhan custom Anda
                        kepada kami.
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  padding: 28px 48px;
                  background: #000000;
                  text-align: center;
                "
              >
                <div
                  style="
                    font-size: 10px;
                    color: #ffcc00;
                    letter-spacing: 5px;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    margin-bottom: 10px;
                  "
                >
                  ✦ Byte Beyond Persona ✦
                </div>
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    font-size: 11px;
                    color: #fefefe;
                    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    font-weight: 300;
                  "
                >
                  Email ini dikirim otomatis setelah pembuatan order custom.<br
                  />
                  Mohon tidak membalas email ini.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td height="5" style="background-color: #ffcc00"></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>